@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_miosvn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v1 + 0.59)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v0 + 0.56 * tmp + 0.95)))
    v1 = wp.cos(0.66)
    v2 = 0.70
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.99) * ((v1 + 0.74 + tmp + 0.19) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.03)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.95 / v2 + 0.30)) / 0.79)
    data[tid] = v0
